    <title type="html"><![CDATA[PromiseTimer 1.8.0]]></title>
    <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<ul dir="auto">
<li>
<p dir="auto">Feature: Add new <code>sleep()</code> function and deprecate <code>resolve()</code> and <code>reject()</code> functions.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1071469949" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/issues/51" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/51/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/51">#51</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-text-html-php"><pre><span class="pl-c">// deprecated</span>
<span class="pl-en"><span class="pl-v">React</span>\<span class="pl-v">Promise</span>\<span class="pl-v">Timer</span>\resolve</span>(<span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c1">$</span>time</span>);
<span class="pl-en"><span class="pl-v">React</span>\<span class="pl-v">Promise</span>\<span class="pl-v">Timer</span>\reject</span>(<span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c1">$</span>time</span>);

<span class="pl-c">// new</span>
<span class="pl-en"><span class="pl-v">React</span>\<span class="pl-v">Promise</span>\<span class="pl-v">Timer</span>\sleep</span>(<span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c1">$</span>time</span>);</pre></div>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">Feature: Support PHP 8.1 release.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1066136114" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/issues/50" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/50/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/50">#50</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/Thomas-Gelf/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/Thomas-Gelf">@Thomas-Gelf</a>, <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1071490423" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/issues/52" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/52/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/52">#52</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a> and <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1053786450" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/issues/48" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/48/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/48">#48</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/SimonFrings/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/SimonFrings">@SimonFrings</a>)</p>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">Improve API documentation and add parameter types and return types.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1065702986" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/issues/49" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/49/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/49">#49</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a> and <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1030130963" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/issues/47" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/47/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-timer/pull/47">#47</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/SimonFrings/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/SimonFrings">@SimonFrings</a>)</p>
</li>
</ul>]]></summary>
