    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Socket 1.10.0]]></title>
    <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<ul dir="auto">
<li>
<p dir="auto">Feature: Support listening on existing file descriptors (FDs) with <code>SocketServer</code>.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="977977806" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/269" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/269/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/269">#269</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-text-html-php"><pre><span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c1">$</span>socket</span> = <span class="pl-k">new</span> <span class="pl-v">React</span>\<span class="pl-v">Socket</span>\<span class="pl-v">SocketSever</span>(<span class="pl-s">'php://fd/3'</span>);</pre></div>
<p dir="auto">This is particularly useful when using<br>
<a href="https://www.freedesktop.org/software/systemd/man/systemd.socket.html" rel="nofollow">systemd socket activation</a><br>
like this:</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-shell"><pre>$ systemd-socket-activate -l 8000 php examples/03-http-server.php php://fd/3</pre></div>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">Feature: Improve error messages for failed connection attempts with <code>errno</code> and <code>errstr</code>.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="963478119" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/265" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/265/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/265">#265</a>, <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="966800966" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/266" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/266/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/266">#266</a>, <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="970373800" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/267" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/267/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/267">#267</a>, <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="987447087" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/270" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/270/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/270">#270</a> and <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="989274583" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/271" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/271/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/271">#271</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a> and <a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="974446521" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/268" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/268/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/268">#268</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/SimonFrings/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/SimonFrings">@SimonFrings</a>)</p>
<p dir="auto">All error messages now always include the appropriate <code>errno</code> and <code>errstr</code> to<br>
give more details about the error reason when available. Along with these<br>
error details exposed by the underlying system functions, it will also<br>
include the appropriate error constant name (such as <code>ECONNREFUSED</code>) when<br>
available. Accordingly, failed TCP/IP connections will now report the actual<br>
underlying error condition instead of a generic "Connection refused" error.<br>
Higher-level error messages will now consistently report the connection URI<br>
scheme and hostname used in all error messages.</p>
<p dir="auto">For most common use cases this means that simply reporting the <code>Exception</code><br>
message should give the most relevant details for any connection issues:</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-text-html-php"><pre><span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c1">$</span>connector</span> = <span class="pl-k">new</span> <span class="pl-v">React</span>\<span class="pl-v">Socket</span>\<span class="pl-v">Connector</span>();
<span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c1">$</span>connector</span>-&gt;<span class="pl-en">connect</span>(<span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c1">$</span>uri</span>)-&gt;<span class="pl-en">then</span>(<span class="pl-k">function</span> (<span class="pl-v">React</span>\<span class="pl-v">Socket</span>\<span class="pl-smi">ConnectionInterface</span> <span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c1">$</span>conn</span>) {
    <span class="pl-c">// …</span>
}, <span class="pl-k">function</span> (<span class="pl-smi">Exception</span> <span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c1">$</span>e</span>) {
    <span class="pl-k">echo</span> <span class="pl-s">'Error:'</span> . <span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c1">$</span>e</span>-&gt;<span class="pl-en">getMessage</span>() . <span class="pl-c1">PHP_EOL</span>;
});</pre></div>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">Improve test suite, test against PHP 8.1 release.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1053759374" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/issues/274" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/socket/pull/274/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/socket/pull/274">#274</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/SimonFrings/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/SimonFrings">@SimonFrings</a>)</p>
</li>
</ul>]]></summary>
