    <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<ul dir="auto">
<li>
<p dir="auto">Feature: Improve error reporting by appending previous exception messages.<br>
(<a class="issue-link js-issue-link" data-error-text="Failed to load title" data-id="1022868983" data-permission-text="Title is private" data-url="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-stream/issues/26" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/reactphp/promise-stream/pull/26/hovercard" href="https://github.com/reactphp/promise-stream/pull/26">#26</a> by <a class="user-mention" data-hovercard-type="user" data-hovercard-url="/users/clue/hovercard" data-octo-click="hovercard-link-click" data-octo-dimensions="link_type:self" href="https://github.com/clue">@clue</a>)</p>
